00/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg>View meaning and origin</div></a><a class=\"group rounded-[1.5rem] border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/62 p-4 backdrop-blur transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-white\" href=\"/names/hindu/vihaan\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-3\"><div><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[color:var(--nv-accent-2)]\">Sanskrit</span><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">Vihaan</h3></div><span class=\"rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-slate-600\">Hindu</span></div><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg>View meaning and origin</div></a></div></div></section><section aria-labelledby=\"authority-title\" class=\"nv-section\"><div class=\"nv-container\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:items-center\"><div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/60 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-3.5 w-3.5 text-[color:var(--nv-accent)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>E-E-A-T for names</div><h2 id=\"authority-title\" class=\"nv-display mt-5 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl\">Built for trustworthy name research.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)] sm:text-lg\">NameVerse combines searchable name data with clear cultural context, origin labels, meaning summaries and internal pathways to deeper research pages.</p><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.5rem] bg-white/62 p-4\"><div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">65K+</div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">Name records</div></div><div class=\"rounded-[1.5rem] bg-white/62 p-4\"><div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">15+</div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">Language roots</div></div><div class=\"rounded-[1.5rem] bg-white/62 p-4\"><div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">Free</div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">Search tools</div></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[2.5rem] border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/62 p-6 backdrop-blur\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote h-8 w-8 text-[color:var(--nv-accent-2)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><p class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">A great name should be easy to search, simple to understand and rich enough to connect a child to family, faith and culture.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">NameVerse homepage sections are designed to answer common parent questions before they leave the page: what names mean, where they come from, which are popular, and how to choose with confidence.</p></div></div></div></section><section aria-labelledby=\"meaning-title\" class=\"nv-section\"><div class=\"nv-container\"><div class=\"rounded-[2.5rem] border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-[color:var(--nv-ink)] p-6 text-white sm:p-8 lg:p-10\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center\"><div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/80\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg>Meaning-led discovery</div><h2 id=\"meaning-title\" class=\"nv-display mt-5 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl\">Baby names with meanings that feel personal.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/72 sm:text-base\">Parents rarely search only for a spelling. They search for values: light, strength, love, peace, blessing, wisdom and courage. NameVerse connects those intent-rich queries to curated search results and origin hubs.</p><div class=\"mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><a class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white/80\" href=\"/search?q=names%20that%20mean%20light\">Names that mean <!-- -->light</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white/80\" href=\"/search?q=names%20that%20mean%20love\">Names that mean <!-- -->love</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white/80\" href=\"/search?q=names%20that%20mean%20strength\">Names that mean <!-- -->strength</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white/80\" href=\"/search?q=names%20that%20mean%20peace\">Names that mean <!-- -->peace</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white/80\" href=\"/search?q=names%20that%20mean%20blessing\">Names that mean <!-- -->blessing</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white/80\" href=\"/search?q=names%20that%20mean%20wisdom\">Names that mean <!-- -->wisdom</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white/80\" href=\"/search?q=names%20that%20mean%20courage\">Names that mean <!-- -->courage</a><a class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white/80\" href=\"/search?q=names%20that%20mean%20grace\">Names that mean <!-- -->grace</a></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white/10 p-5 transition hover:bg-white/16\" href=\"/names-by-meaning\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-library h-6 w-6 text-white/90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m16 6 4 14\"></path><path d=\"M12 6v14\"></path><path d=\"M8 8v12\"></path><path d=\"M4 4v16\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold\">Meaning index</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/68\">Find names by semantic theme and cultural interpretation.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white/10 p-5 transition hover:bg-white/16\" href=\"/name-meanings\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe h-6 w-6 text-white/90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold\">Origin explorer</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/68\">Browse Arabic, Urdu, Persian, Sanskrit, Hebrew and Greek roots.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white/10 p-5 transition hover:bg-white/16\" href=\"/trending-names\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flame h-6 w-6 text-white/90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 3q1 4 4 6.5t3 5.5a1 1 0 0 1-14 0 5 5 0 0 1 1-3 1 1 0 0 0 5 0c0-2-1.5-3-1.5-5q0-2 2.5-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold\">Trending names</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/68\">Discover names gaining search interest across traditions.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-[1.75rem] bg-white/10 p-5 transition hover:bg-white/16\" href=\"/search\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search h-6 w-6 text-white/90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-base font-bold\">Advanced search</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/68\">Search names, meanings, origins, religions and gender.</p></a></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"homepage-faq\" aria-labelledby=\"faq-title\" class=\"nv-section\"><div class=\"nv-container\"><div class=\"mb-8 flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/60 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-3.5 w-3.5 text-[color:var(--nv-accent-2)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>FAQ</div><h2 id=\"faq-title\" class=\"nv-display mt-5 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl\">Answers parents ask before choosing a name.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)] sm:text-lg\">Homepage FAQ content is written for real search intent and marked up as FAQPage schema.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-2\"><details class=\"nv-surface rounded-[2rem] p-5\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">How do I find the best baby name with meaning?</summary><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">Start by searching a name, meaning, origin, religion or theme. NameVerse connects each query to curated name lists, cultural context and related browsing paths so you can compare options quickly.</p></details><details class=\"nv-surface rounded-[2rem] p-5\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">Which baby names are trending in 2026?</summary><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">Parents are searching for short, meaningful and globally pronounceable names. Popular homepage picks include Muhammad, Aisha, Rayan, Noah, Olivia, Aarav, Diya and Ananya, with more options in the trending names hub.</p></details><details class=\"nv-surface rounded-[2rem] p-5\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">Can I search names by religion, origin or meaning?</summary><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">Yes. Browse Islamic, Hindu and Christian names by religion, then narrow by origins such as Arabic, Urdu, Persian, Sanskrit, Hebrew, Greek or Latin. You can also search meanings such as light, love, strength or peace.</p></details><details class=\"nv-surface rounded-[2rem] p-5\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">Are NameVerse meanings verified?</summary><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">NameVerse prioritizes verified meanings and cultural context. Entries are reviewed for linguistic origin, common usage and faith-aware interpretation before being surfaced in search and curated lists.</p></details><details class=\"nv-surface rounded-[2rem] p-5\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)]\">Is NameVerse free to use?</summary><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">Yes. NameVerse search, name meanings, browsing pages, FAQs and name discovery tools are free for parents, families and researchers.</p></details></div></div></section><section aria-labelledby=\"articles-title\" class=\"nv-section\"><div class=\"nv-container\"><div class=\"mb-8 flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/60 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-3.5 w-3.5 text-[color:var(--nv-accent-2)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>Expert guidance</div><h2 id=\"articles-title\" class=\"nv-display mt-5 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl\">Latest NameVerse articles.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)] sm:text-lg\">Editorial content supports topical authority, long-tail discovery and parent confidence.</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/62 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] backdrop-blur transition hover:bg-white\" href=\"/blog\">View all articles<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/60 p-8 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-[color:var(--nv-muted)]\">Loading latest articles…</div><!--/$--></div></section><section aria-label=\"Homepage final CTA\" class=\"nv-section pb-10\"><div class=\"nv-container\"><div class=\"rounded-[2.5rem] border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/62 p-6 text-center backdrop-blur sm:p-10\"><h2 class=\"nv-display text-3xl font-semibold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] sm:text-4xl\">Find a name with meaning, origin and confidence.</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--nv-muted)] sm:text-base\">Start with a name, explore by meaning, or browse a cultural tradition. NameVerse is built to make name research fast, clear and trustworthy.</p><div class=\"mt-6 flex flex-col justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-[color:var(--nv-ink)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800\" href=\"/search\">Search names<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-[color:var(--nv-border)] bg-white/70 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-[color:var(--nv-ink)] transition hover:bg-white\" href=\"/names/religion/islamic/1\">Browse Islamic names</a></div></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class=\"border-t border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 text-white\"><img alt=\"NameVerse logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/logo.png\"/></div><div><div class=\"text-lg font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950\">NameVerse</div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500\">Meanings, origins &amp; guides</div></div></a><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">NameVerse helps parents and researchers discover baby names with meanings, cultural origins, linguistic context and trusted naming guidance.</p><div class=\"mt-6 flex gap-2\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/NameVerseOfficial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-slate-600 transition hover:border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-700\" aria-label=\"Twitter\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-share2 lucide-share-2 h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"5\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"19\" r=\"3\"></circle><line x1=\"8.59\" x2=\"15.42\" y1=\"13.51\" y2=\"17.49\"></line><line x1=\"15.41\" x2=\"8.59\" y1=\"6.51\" y2=\"10.49\"></line></svg></a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-slate-600 transition hover:border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-700\" aria-label=\"Facebook\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-slate-600 transition hover:border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-700\" aria-label=\"Instagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link2 lucide-link-2 h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 17H7A5 5 0 0 1 7 7h2\"></path><path d=\"M15 7h2a5 5 0 1 1 0 10h-2\"></path><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line></svg></a><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-slate-600 transition hover:border-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-50 hover:text-blue-700\" aria-label=\"LinkedIn\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></a></div></div><div><h3 class=\"mb-4 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-slate-950\">By Religion</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 transition hover:text-blue-700\" href=\"/islamic/boy-names\">Islamic Names</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 transitio